In the Matter of the Bankruptcy of the INTERNATIONAL MORTGAGE TRUST COMPANY, a Corporation, State of Kansas, ex rel. Roland Boynton, Attorney General, et al., Petitioners. No. 659. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. May 25, 1933. O’Neil & Hamilton, of Topeka, Kan., for petitioners.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Petition dismissed on motion of petitioners.
